245
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:46,700
Netreba.

246
00:23:49,810 --> 00:23:51,100
Poďme jesť.

247
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,400
Čo?

248
00:23:52,910 --> 00:23:54,350
Poďme na večeru.

249
00:23:54,610 --> 00:23:56,200
Keď sme sa takto stretli.

250
00:23:56,810 --> 00:24:00,000
Poďme sa najesť ako bratia a sestry.

251
00:24:04,120 --> 00:24:05,200
Poďme.

252
00:24:07,120 --> 00:24:09,200
Dobre, poďme.

253
00:24:11,730 --> 00:24:13,500
Nechcem, ja nepôjdem.

254
00:24:15,630 --> 00:24:17,200
Mal si ísť so mnou!

255
00:24:17,630 --> 00:24:20,000
Prečo to musia byť zrazu 4?

256
00:24:21,940 --> 00:24:23,000
Nechcem.

257
00:24:28,140 --> 00:24:31,000
Ha Na, si v poriadku? Ukáž mi to.

258
00:24:31,350 --> 00:24:33,000
Som v poriadku.

259
00:24:38,350 --> 00:24:39,100
Čo je?

260
00:24:39,450 --> 00:24:41,000
Bolí ma noha.

261
